

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <!-- 引用google字體 -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!--  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <!-- 引用fontawesome icon -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/da3a6ce48e.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/jquery.js"></script>
    <title>專欄報導</title>

    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .column-main {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #000;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 50%;
        }

        .page {
            transform: translateX(-110%);
            position: absolute;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            transition: .5s;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center center;
        }

        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 10%;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 30px;
            border-bottom: #fff 4px solid;
            text-align: center;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            margin: 50px;
            left: calc(50% + (var(--i)*17%));
            z-index: 999;
            transition: .3s;
        }

        .page-content {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 50px;
            color: #fff;
            position: absolute;
            left: 100%;
            display: none;
            animation-name: fade;
            animation-iteration-count: 1;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        @@keyframes fade {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            50% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-50px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0px);
            }
        }

        input {
            display: none;
        }

        input:checked+.page {
            transform: translateX(0px);
            transition: .4s;
        }

        input:checked+.page .page-content {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }

        .page:nth-child(3) {
            background-image: url(/img/column01.jpg);
            background-position: center;
        }

        .page:nth-child(3) .page-content {
            background-color: rgb(185, 130, 130);
        }

        .page:nth-child(6) {
            background-image: url(/img/column02.jpg);
        }

        .page:nth-child(6) .page-content {
            background-color: rgb(170, 170, 226);
        }

        .page:nth-child(9) {
            background-image: url(/img/column03.jpg);
        }

        .page:nth-child(9) .page-content {
            background-color: rgb(236, 180, 110);
        }

        .page h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
        }

        .page p {
            font-size: 30px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0, .3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .page span {
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #f6f6e9;
        }

        label:hover {
            cursor: pointer;
            border-bottom: solid 4px rgb(35, 35, 35);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    

    <div class="column-main">
        <label for="button1" class="button" style="--i:0">專欄一</label>
        <input type="radio" name="page" id="button1" checked>
        <div class="page">
            <div class="page-content">
                <h1>這是狗界雙胞胎？</h1>
                <!-- <p>可愛的狗勾</p> -->
                <span>
                    到現在也快八個月了，從小一起長大
                    <br/>
                    常常會同時間有做一樣的動作
                    <br/>
                    或是有一樣的表情
                    同時間尿尿、同時間便便
                    <br/>
                    更別說同時間吃飯喝水
                    <br/>
                    原來我是養了兩個小孩才對!
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <label for="button2" class="button" style="--i:1">專欄二</label>
        <input type="radio" name="page" id="button2">
        <div class="page">
            <div class="page-content">
                <h1>耐心等待的狗狗!</h1>
                <span>
                    當主人進商店購買時
                    <br/>
                    把狗狗綁在了外面
                    <br/>
                    可狗完全沒有任何吠叫!!!
                    <br/>
                    難道這就是...有家教的狗嗎!?
                    <br/>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <label for="button3" class="button" style="--i:2">專欄三</label>
        <input type="radio" name="page" id="button3">
        <div class="page">
            <div class="page-content">
                <h1>希望你能一直陪我</h1>
                <span>
                    今年你已經八歲了
                    <br/>
                    一想到你越來越老，身體越來越虛弱
                    <br/>
                    就會覺得很難過
                    <br/>
                    可當你搖著尾巴蹭著我時
                    <br/>
                    我又會覺得很開心有你陪伴
                    <br/>
                    希望時間能過慢一點，讓我們相處更久
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</body>

</html>